  <brief_title>Evaluate ALLN-177 in Patients With Enteric Hyperoxaluria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of ALLN-177 in Patients With Enteric Hyperoxaluria: A Phase III Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
